variant_descriptions.KANDNW: Bitwise AND NOT 16 bits masks k2 and k3 and place result in k1.
variant_descriptions.KANDNB: Bitwise AND NOT 8 bits masks k1 and k2 and place result in k1.
variant_descriptions.KANDNQ: Bitwise AND NOT 64 bits masks k2 and k3 and place result in k1.
variant_descriptions.KANDND: Bitwise AND NOT 32 bits masks k2 and k3 and place result in k1.

op.text: Performs a bitwise AND NOT between the vector mask k2 and the vector mask k3, and writes the result into vector mask k1.
